<br>
If you run away from the party, I'm not going to chase you down to heal you.  If the choice is between being able to heal you as you run away, or being able to heal the rest of the party as they deal with the pulled creatures, I'm going to stay near the party to heal them.<br>
<br>
Further, I have absolutely no remorse for people in my party who die because they panicked, ran away, and then got killed, especially when I punch my heal hotkey (which announces that I'm trying to heal you to the group) twice.<br>
<br>
Please, learn this: stick close to your party's healers.  Only bards can run and &quot;cast&quot; at the same time. <p>"These discourses of heterosexuality oppress us in the sense that they prevent us from speaking unless we speak in their terms."<BR>
