<br>
It's basically : See the little half see through wolfy?  That's my friend.  He does a little more damage than I tend to do with my own weapons.  That's why I send him out instead of me when I'm primary healer.  That way I contribute to the distruction of the mob while making sure everyone stays healed and I make sure I have enough mana for these heals.  I am not trying to be lazy, if I was I wouldn't summon this wolf.  I am making an attempt to make sure you stay alive.  If you do not understand this or don't like my method, that's your choice, but I've found it the best way to work things.<br>
